ps://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMCI\" title=\"Super Micro Computer, Inc.\">SMCI</a></span>), also called Supermicro, was on October 17, 2024; I issued a sell call because of a potential DoJ investigation and accounting concerns brought up by a </span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742698-super-micro-computer-smci-navigating-risks-holds-promise-bold-investors-upgrade-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 21:20:20"}, {"id": "4742695", "title": "Uber: Biggest Money Is Made When Reasonable Worries Are Exaggerated, My Top Pick For 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Uber logo inscriptioned on a white painted car. Uber car in traffic.\" data-id=\"1284409813\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4448px\" height=\"3271px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Cristi Croitoru</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Uber Technologies (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UBER\" title=\"Uber Technologies, Inc.\">UBER</a></span>) is arguably the cheapest growth stock in the market today, trading at 28 times '25 earnings and a 4.5% free cash flow yield, on expectations for mid-teens revenue growth for years to come.</p> <p>The</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284409813/image_1284409813.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742695-uber-biggest-money-is-made-when-reasonable-worries-are-exaggerated", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 21:15:37"}, {"id": "4742666", "title": "Undercovered Dozen: PagerDuty, SUSS MicroTek, High Tide, 8x8 +", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Doughnuts\" data-id=\"155376667\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">pjohnson1/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Undercovered Dozen Introduction</h2> <p>The 'Undercovered' Dozen is a weekly Seeking Alpha editor-curated series highlighting 12 articles on lesser covered stocks from the previous seven days. We hope this provides ideas and inspires discussion among the community.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742666-undercovered-dozen-pagerduty-suss-microtek-high-tide-8x8-plus", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 21:10:37"}, {"id": "4742680", "title": "Salesforce: What 2024 Taught Us About Market Expectations", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Salesforce logo at its Corporate office in New York, NY, USA on August 18, 2022.\" data-id=\"1610021131\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_161002113